  <title>Ex-Deutsche Bank MD appointed to run Chi-X</title>
  <content>
Chi-X has hired Deutsche Bank's former local co-head of markets to run its Australian arm. 
Vic Jokovic, who left Deutsche Bank after 26-year earlier this year, was announced as Chi-X Australia chief executive officer on Thursday morning. 
